name: About Lines #6: Equilibrium
description:
After the universe, the equilibrium. A peaceful conversation between the conceivable and the eternally unknown.

This piece is part of a series inspired by Japanese calligraphy and the works of German-French painter Hans Hartung (1904 - 1989).

PNG, 7200 × 4500 px · Original artwork by Andreas Rau · Oslo, 2021
